---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Applied AI in Marketing | Steve R Gibson";
const description =
    "Detailed frameworks for AI Audience Engines, Feed-Driven DCO, and Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) with real-world examples.";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={description}>
    <!-- Mermaid JS for Diagrams -->
    <script type="module" is:inline>
        import mermaid from "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.esm.min.mjs";
        mermaid.initialize({
            startOnLoad: true,
            theme: "base",
            securityLevel: "loose",
            themeVariables: {
                darkMode: true,
                primaryColor: "#2563eb", // blue-600
                lineColor: "#94a3b8", // slate-400
                secondaryColor: "#1e293b", // slate-800
                tertiaryColor: "#0f172a", // slate-950
            },
        });
    </script>

    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10 dark:opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
    >
        <svg class="h-full w-full" width="100%" height="100%">
            <defs>
                <pattern
                    id="grid-pattern"
                    width="40"
                    height="40"
                    patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M0 40L40 0H20L0 20M40 40V20L20 40"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        fill="none"
                        class="text-blue-500"></path>
                </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid-pattern)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <section class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-24 py-16 px-4">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <header class="text-center space-y-8">
            <span
                class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase"
            >
                Proprietary Methodologies
            </span>
            <h1
                class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight"
            >
                Applied AI in <br /><span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600"
                    >Marketing</span
                >
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
            >
                Moving beyond the hype. These are the engineered systems I
                deploy to turn algorithmic chaos into predictable revenue
                growth.
            </p>
        </header>

        <!-- Framework 1: AI Audience Engine -->
        <article class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                    class="p-3 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-xl text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 shrink-0 mt-1"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"
                        ></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path
                            d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path
                            d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                    >
                        01. AI Audience Engine
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                        Predictive targeting based on business truth, not vanity
                        metrics.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 pl-0 md:pl-20"
            >
                <p>
                    The era of static demographic targeting is dead. The <strong
                        >AI Audience Engine</strong
                    > is a closed-loop system that ingests first-party CRM data to
                    train ad platform algorithms (Google, Meta) on who your <em
                        >actual</em
                    > best customers are, not just who clicks your ads.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Real World Example Card -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden ml-0 md:ml-20"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-widest"
                >
                    Real World Application
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                >
                    The "Tier-1" Legal Revenue Model
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The Challenge
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                A national firm was drowning in "cheap
                                leads"â€”users searching for "free legal advice"
                                who had no intent to hire. Volume was high, but
                                revenue was stagnant.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The AI Solution
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                We built a pipeline connecting <strong
                                    >Salesforce</strong
                                > directly to <strong>Google Ads OCT</strong>.
                                We stopped optimizing for "Form Fills" and
                                started optimizing for "Retainer Signed".
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4 font-mono text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >
                        IF lead_score > 80 AND status = 'Consultation_Booked' <br
                        />
                        THEN fire_conversion_event(value=$3500) <br />
                        ELSE suppress_audience_signal
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pt-6"
                    >
                        <h4
                            class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4"
                        >
                            The Outcome
                        </h4>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div
                                class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30 text-center"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
                                >
                                    +40%
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1"
                                >
                                    Qualified Case Vol
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-900/30 text-center"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400"
                                >
                                    -15%
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1"
                                >
                                    Ad Spend
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Measurement Stack Diagram Integration -->
            <div class="mt-8 ml-0 md:ml-20">
                <div
                    class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-700"
                >
                    <!-- Terminal Header -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-800 px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-slate-700"
                    >
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                        <div
                            class="flex-1 text-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-400"
                        >
                            conversion_logic.mermaid
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 overflow-x-auto">
                        <div class="mermaid flex justify-center">
                            flowchart TD CAC["CAC<br /><span
                                style="font-weight:normal; font-size:10px"
                                >Cost Per Lead</span
                            >"] --> CPQL["CPQL<br /><span
                                style="font-weight:normal; font-size:10px"
                                >Qualified Cost</span
                            >"] CPQL --> REV["Revenue<br /><span
                                style="font-weight:normal; font-size:10px"
                                >Actual Cash</span
                            >"] REV --> LTV["LTV<br /><span
                                style="font-weight:normal; font-size:10px"
                                >Lifetime Profit</span
                            >"] style CAC fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
                            style CPQL fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
                            style REV fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
                            style LTV fill:#2563eb,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#fff
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800" />

        <!-- Framework 2: Feed-Driven DCO -->
        <article class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                    class="p-3 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 rounded-xl text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-1"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path
                            d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"
                        ></path><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"
                        ></polyline><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"
                        ></line></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                    >
                        02. Feed-Driven DCO
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                        Dynamic Creative Optimization that scales relevance
                        without manual labor.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 pl-0 md:pl-20"
            >
                <p>
                    Standard DCO tests colors and headlines. <strong
                        >Feed-Driven DCO</strong
                    > injects real-time business intelligence into your ads. By linking
                    your ad creative to a live data feed (inventory, capacity, local
                    pricing), you ensure that you never pay for a click you can't
                    service.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Real World Example Card -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden ml-0 md:ml-20"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-purple-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-widest"
                >
                    Real World Application
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                >
                    Hyper-Local Capacity Management
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The Challenge
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                A multi-location service business was wasting
                                budget driving leads to local branches that were
                                already fully booked for the week.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The AI Solution
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                We created a "Capacity Feed" that monitored
                                calendar availability in real-time. This feed
                                powered a Dynamic Ad Template.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
                        <div
                            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                        >
                            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-green-600 mb-1">
                                SCENARIO A: Openings Available
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white"
                            >
                                "Book a [Service] in [City]. 3 Appointments open
                                for tomorrow!"
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 opacity-75"
                        >
                            <div class="text-xs font-bold text-red-500 mb-1">
                                SCENARIO B: Fully Booked
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 italic"
                            >
                                [Ad Group Automatically Paused]
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pt-6"
                    >
                        <h4
                            class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4"
                        >
                            The Outcome
                        </h4>
                        <div
                            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-100 dark:border-purple-900/30 text-center"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400"
                            >
                                100%
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1"
                            >
                                Budget Utilization on Need
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800" />

        <!-- Framework 3: GEO -->
        <article class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                    class="p-3 bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900 rounded-xl text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-300 shrink-0 mt-1"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path
                            d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                    >
                        03. Generative Engine Optimization
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                        Structuring your brand to be "The Answer" in the AI
                        search era.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 pl-0 md:pl-20"
            >
                <p>
                    SEO was about links and keywords. <strong
                        >GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)</strong
                    > is about Entity Authority and Citation Density. It's the art
                    of structuring your brand's digital footprint so that Large Language
                    Models (LLMs) like ChatGPT, Claude, and Gemini recognize your
                    brand as the factual authority in your niche.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Real World Example Card -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden ml-0 md:ml-20"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-widest"
                >
                    Real World Application
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                >
                    Winning the "Zero-Click" Search
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The Challenge
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                Users stopping at the "Answer Box" or asking AI
                                chatbots for recommendations instead of clicking
                                through to websites.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The AI Solution
                            </h4>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                I mapped the <strong
                                    >7-Stage AI Search Journey</strong
                                > and optimized content specifically for the "Solution
                                Seeking" and "AI Verification" phases.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 7-Stage Diagram Integration -->
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <div
                            class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-slate-700"
                        >
                            <!-- Terminal Header -->
                            <div
                                class="bg-slate-800 px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-slate-700"
                            >
                                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500">
                                </div>
                                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500">
                                </div>
                                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500">
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="flex-1 text-center text-xs font-mono text-slate-400"
                                >
                                    search_journey.mermaid
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-6 overflow-x-auto">
                                <div class="mermaid flex justify-center">
                                    flowchart TD A["1. Unaware<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Algorithmic Feed Exposure</span
                                    >"] --> B["2. Problem Aware<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Natural Language Query</span
                                    >"] B --> C["3. Solution Seeking<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >AI Synthesis & RAG</span
                                    >"] C --> D["4. AI Verification<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Agent Checks Reviews/Trust</span
                                    >"] D --> E["5. Brand Comparison<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Feature Matrix Generation</span
                                    >"] E --> F["6. Human Validation<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Cultural & Vibe Check</span
                                    >"] F --> G["7. Decision<br /><span
                                        style="font-weight:normal; font-size:12px"
                                        >Conversion</span
                                    >"] style A
                                    fill:#1e293b,stroke:#334155,color:#fff style
                                    B fill:#1e293b,stroke:#334155,color:#fff
                                    style C
                                    fill:#1e293b,stroke:#334155,color:#fff style
                                    D
                                    fill:#2563eb,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
                                    style E
                                    fill:#1e293b,stroke:#334155,color:#fff style
                                    F fill:#1e293b,stroke:#334155,color:#fff
                                    style G
                                    fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pt-6"
                    >
                        <h4
                            class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4"
                        >
                            The Outcome
                        </h4>
                        <div
                            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-900/30 text-center"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400"
                            >
                                +300%
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mt-1"
                            >
                                Brand Mentions in AI Answers
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800" />

        <!-- Framework 4: Content Personalization -->
        <article class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                    class="p-3 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900 rounded-xl text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-300 shrink-0 mt-1"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M12 2.69l5.66 5.66a8 8 0 1 1-11.31 0z"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2"
                    >
                        04. AI-Driven Content Personalization
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
                        Moving beyond "Hi [Name]" to "Here is exactly what you
                        need right now."
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 pl-0 md:pl-20"
            >
                <p>
                    Generic newsletters are ignored. <strong
                        >AI-Driven Personalization</strong
                    > analyzes behavioral signals to construct unique content experiences
                    for each prospect. It's not just swapping names; it's dynamically
                    assembling entire value propositions based on what the user has
                    actually read, watched, and clicked.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Real World Example Card -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden ml-0 md:ml-20"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-widest"
                >
                    Real World Application
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                >
                    The "Hyper-Relevant" B2B Nurture
                </h3>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <h4
                                class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1"
                            >
                                The Challenge
